振り返る伊吹桂子。\r\n死んでしまった岡部絵美のこと、祖母のこと……。\r\n「あんたは少しお直しが必要だね」\r\n祖母は桂子を見て、そう言った。\r\n\r\n脚本：中西やすひろ\r\n絵コンテ：銀さん\r\n演出：森洸貴\r\n総作画監督：濱田邦彦\r\n作画監督：銀さん、DR MOVIE (Go Yu-il、Kim Bong-deok、Park Jae-seok、Sin Seong-min、Jo Mi-jeong、Han Seung-jin)","ep":3,"sort":3,"id":1653785,"subject_id":493724,"comment":225,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":1420},{"airdate":"2026-04-30","name":"四方木田かよと山県沙織 / 田畑若菜と田畑佐江子 / 柏木拓人と吉村さやか","name_cn":"四方木田佳代与山县纱织／田畑若菜与田畑佐江子／柏木拓人与吉村清日","duration":"00:23:40","desc":"淡島に来られなかった者、別の道へ進む者、女優の道を進み続ける者……。\r\n若菜は絹枝の語った過去を思い出す。\r\n「あたしが淡島にいる意味。もっとちゃんと考えよう」\r\n\r\n脚本：綾奈ゆにこ\r\n絵コンテ・演出：いしづかあつこ\r\n総作画監督：濱田邦彦\r\n作画監督：西田亜沙子、川口裕子、藤澤俊幸","ep":4,"sort":4,"id":1653786,"subject_id":493724,"comment":65,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":1420},{"airdate":"2026-05-07","name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"00:23:40","desc":"","ep":5,"sort":5,"id":1653787,"subject_id":493724,"comment":1,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":1420},{"airdate":"2026-05-14","name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"00:23:40","desc":"","ep":6,"sort":6,"id":1653788,"subject_id":493724,"comment":0,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":1420},{"airdate":"2026-05-21","name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"00:23:40","desc":"","ep":7,"sort":7,"id":1653789,"subject_id":493724,"comment":0,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":1420},{"airdate":"2026-05-28","name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"00:23:40","desc":"","ep":8,"sort":8,"id":1653790,"subject_id":493724,"comment":0,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":1420},{"airdate":"2026-06-04","name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"00:23:40","desc":"","ep":9,"sort":9,"id":1653791,"subject_id":493724,"comment":0,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":1420},{"airdate":"2026-06-11","name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"00:23:40","desc":"","ep":10,"sort":10,"id":1653792,"subject_id":493724,"comment":0,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":1420},{"airdate":"2026-06-18","name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"00:23:40","desc":"","ep":11,"sort":11,"id":1653793,"subject_id":493724,"comment":0,"type":0,"di